quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  16,41,"Abo bafudukayo ngenxa yokukholisa uAllâh, emva kokuba babenziwe ubugwenxa, Siya kubanika ngokwenene indawo yokuhlala elungileyo kweli hlabathi, kodwa wona umvuzo welizayo uya kuba mkhulu ngakumbi ukuba bebesazi"
  16,42,"(Abo ke) ngabo baba nomonde, babeka ithemba labo eNkosini yabo"
  16,43,"Kananjalo ASizanga Sithumele ngaphambili kunawe nantoni na ngaphandle kwamadoda, eSawathumelela isiTyhilelo. Ke kaloku buzani kubantu abanolwazi lwesiBhalo, ukuba anazi"
  16,44,"Ngemiqondiso ecacileyo neNcwadi (Sathumela abaProfeti) Sathumela kananjalo kuwe (Muhammad) iDthikr (i’Kur’ân), khon’ukuze uchazele abantu ngokucacileyo oko kuthunyelwe kubo, kwanokuba bacingisise"
  16,45,"Ingaba abo baqulunqa amayelenqe angcolileyo baziva bekhuselekile na okokuba uAllâh Akayi kubatshonisa bazike emhlabeni, okanye isohlwayo asiyi kubahlasela kumacala abangawalindelanga"
  16,46,"Okanye Ababambe phakathi besaya okanye bebuya (emisebenzini yabo), ukuze bangabi nakuphuncula (esohlwayweni sika-Allâh)"
  16,47,"Okanye Ababambe ngokuya bemosha ngokumosha (ubutyebi babo). Inene! INkosi yenu InobuBele, nguSozinceba"
  16,48,"Kanti abaziqwalaseli na izinto ezidalwe nguAllâh: (indlela) eziba ngasekunene ngayo nasekhohlo ngayo izithunzi zazo, ziqubude kuAllâh, zibe zithobekile"
  16,49,"Ke kaloku kuAllâh kuqubuda zonke izinto ezisezulwini nasemhlabeni. Ezizizidalwa ezinyakazayo neengelosi, yaye azikhukhumali"
  16,50,Zona zoyika iNkosi yazo phezu kwazo yaye zenza loo nto ziyalelwe yona